					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-634246#post-4562996</guid>
				<title>Staff Post - Open</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-634246/scp-1498#post-4562996</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2020 16:59:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Elogee FishTruck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4037075</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The first image that was used in this article has been replaced with an image that's cc-compliant with the SCP wiki's license (CC BY-SA 3.0) and is sourced as follows:</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Title:</strong> download-new.jpg<br /> <strong>Author(s):</strong> Eugenio Hansen, OFS, Nition1, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594389282" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" >Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594389282" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span><br /> <strong>Release year:</strong> 2020<br /> <strong>Note:</strong> Created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594389282" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" >Elogee FishTruck</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594389282" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span> utilizing the images below as components in the final image</p> <hr /> <p><strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:EXPOINTER_2013_01_Sheep.JPG">Wikimedia Commons</a><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY-SA 3.0<br /> <strong>Title:</strong> EXPOINTER 2013&#160;01 Sheep.JPG<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> Eugenio Hansen, OFS</p> <hr /> <p><strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:New_Zealand_Rotary_Telephone.jpg">Wikimedia Commons</a><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY-SA 3.0<br /> <strong>Title:</strong> New Zealand Rotary Telephone.jpg<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> Nition1</p> </blockquote> <p>The second image that was used in this article is non-compliant with the SCP wiki's license (CC BY-SA 3.0) as it comes from the <a href="http://www.surrealistball.nl/">Surrealist Ball</a> with no indication it has been released under Creative Commons. Thus, the image has been removed.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
