				<wikidot:authorName>Lumancer</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>662776</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Lethally self-propagating items like this tend to annoy me, but the mention of a &quot;collective&quot; sent my headcanon spinning. I have to think the consciousness of each &quot;victim&quot; is actually ending up in a decent situation once the effect has run its course. Or, at the very least, being given an interesting employment opportunity&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
